description: Demolition of existing commercial units and erection of 3 x four-storey blocks and 1 x five-storey block, comprising 120 self-contained flats, 1,823m of commercial floorspace (Use Class B1) and 5 live/work units, with 86 car-parking spaces, bicycle and bin storage and associated landscaping (accompanied by Design and Access Statement, Energy Assessment, Noise Assessment, Flood Risk Assessment, Arboricultural Report, Transportation Assessment and Planning Statement), subject to a Deed of Agreement dated 13/08/2008 under Section 106 of the Town and Country Planning Act 1990 (as amended)
